                Pompeius <lb n="2"/>Agilis <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> sibi <lb n="3"/>et Pompeiae <lb n="4"/>Primigeniae <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXV et <lb n="6"/>Pompeiae Spectatae <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XVII <lb n="8"/>et Couriae <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XVI <lb n="9"/>et Sextiae Suputae <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et Vitali <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili--</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XX
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1-9 von Halbsäulen eingefasst; Z. 10 befindet sich darunter auf dem oberen Rahmen eines Bildfeldes mit Adlern, die eine Girlande halten.</p>
